Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer at 4Geeks Academy is a course that allows you to start a career as a data scientist and build your first ML models. The course duration is 16 weeks and includes classes 3 times a week. It has a small class size of maximum 12 people. No previous experience is needed and you can choose between English and Spanish for the syllabus and content. The instructors for this course include Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. They have extensive experience in the field of AI and machine learning. You will learn Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, and create predictive models using libraries like Pandas and Numpy. The course also focuses on mastering industry-standard tools and developing your own AI projects. The certificates provided by 4Geeks Academy are recognized by multiple organizations. For more information, visit the website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop